{"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistrationFailure:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Handles push notification registration failure.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The NSError received from APNs registration failure"}]}],"name":"error"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application:didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to notify Pushwoosh about registration failures."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This allows Pushwoosh to:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Log the error for debugging"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Retry registration if appropriate","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Update device status in the Control Panel"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration failure with user feedback:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError error: Error) {","","        \/\/ Forward to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistrationFailure(error as NSError)","","        \/\/ Log for debugging","        Logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","","        \/\/ Handle specific error cases","        let nsError = error as NSError","        switch nsError.code {","        case 3010:","            \/\/ Simulator or push not supported","            Logger.warning(\"Push notifications not supported on this device\")","","        default:","            \/\/ Track error in analytics","            Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                \"error_code\": nsError.code,","                \"error_message\": nsError.localizedDescription","            ])","","            \/\/ Optionally notify user","            if shouldShowPushError {","                showPushRegistrationError()","            }","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handlePushRegistrationFailure:":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles push notification registration failure."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","abstract":[]}}}